Navistar - Global Portfolio - Products - Trucks












































Trucks BusesDefense VehiclesEngines








TRUCK

Navistar offers one of the world's premier and most trusted truck brands.  International Truck offers state-of-the-art performance and solutions for a variety of global markets.  International Truck, the flagship vehicle brand, is supported by the industry's largest dealer network and offers a complete lineup of integrated vehicles.











TRUCK BRANDS
International TrucksInternational® Truck is Navistar’s flagship vehicle brand and offers a complete lineup of integrated vehicles ranging from class 4-8. International® Truck prides itself on knowing and understanding its customers’ needs, and delivers solutions that help every one of its customers’ businesses run at its best.Visit Site















